### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

###

### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Fellowship of the Ring",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "978-0261103573",
  "publishedYear": 1954
}

###

### Create a review for book ID 1 (Nested Post)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerName": "Alan",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "An absolute masterpiece of fantasy literature!"
}

###

### Get all books again (Should now include the reviews nested inside book ID 1!)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
